msgid "Is Duka Mwecheche free?"
msgstr "Is Duka Mwecheche free?"

msgid "Yes! The platform is completely free for all businesses. You only pay standard M-Pesa transaction fees when accepting payments."
msgstr "Yes! The platform is completely free for all businesses. You only pay standard M-Pesa transaction fees when accepting payments."

msgid "Do I need a smartphone?"
msgstr "Do I need a smartphone?"

msgid "No. You can manage your stock via USSD on any basic phone. The web app works on smartphones and computers too."
msgstr "No. You can manage your stock via USSD on any basic phone. The web app works on smartphones and computers too."

msgid "How do customers find my shop?"
msgstr "How do customers find my shop?"

msgid "Once you register and add items with prices, your business appears on the Marketplace. Customers can search by location and product."
msgstr "Once you register and add items with prices, your business appears on the Marketplace. Customers can search by location and product."

msgid "Is my data safe?"
msgstr "Is my data safe?"

msgid "Absolutely. Your data is stored securely on cloud servers with regular backups. Only you and your staff can access your business data."
msgstr "Absolutely. Your data is stored securely on cloud servers with regular backups. Only you and your staff can access your business data."

msgid "Can I accept M-Pesa payments?"
msgstr "Can I accept M-Pesa payments?"

msgid "Yes. We integrate with Safaricom's Daraja API. You'll need a Till or Paybill number from Safaricom to receive funds directly."
msgstr "Yes. We integrate with Safaricom's Daraja API. You'll need a Till or Paybill number from Safaricom to receive funds directly."

msgid "How do I add staff?"
msgstr "How do I add staff?"

msgid "Go to Manage -> Staff -> Add Staff. Staff members can record transactions but cannot access business settings or financial reports."
msgstr "Go to Manage -> Staff -> Add Staff. Staff members can record transactions but cannot access business settings or financial reports."

